n Wonderland (  1865 ) and Through the Looking Glass (  1872 ), who was based on his child friend  Alice Liddell , daughter of the Dean of Christ Church, Oxford."],"variants":[{"name":"Alys","meanings":["Variant spelling of   Alice ."]},{"name":"Alis","meanings":["equivalent of <b>Alice</b> ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Alice Laton was born in 1444, in Lancashire, England, United Kingdom. She had at least 1 daughter with Sir John Thornborough. She died in 1500, in Essex, England, United Kingdom, at the age of 56."},"et":{"1444–1500":"1444–1500","1440–1531":"1440–1531","1467–Female":"1467–Surnud","1467":"1467","1500":"1500","1444":"1444","1531":"1531","1440":"1440","Lancashire, England":"Lancashire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Essex, England, United Kingdom":"Essex, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Southampton, Hampshire, England":"Southampton, Hampshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1444–1500":"1444–1500","1440–1531":"1440–1531","1467–Female":"1467–Kuollut","1467":"1467","1500":"1500","1444":"1444","1531":"1531","1440":"1440","Lancashire, England":"Lancashire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Essex, England, United Kingdom":"Essex, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Southampton, Hampshire, England":"Southampton, Hampshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1444–1500":"1444–1500","1440–1531":"1440–1531","1467–Female":"1467–Décédée","1467":"1467","1500":"1500","1444":"1444","1531":"1531","1440":"1440","Lancashire, England":"Lancashire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Essex, England, United Kingdom":"Essex, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Southampton, Hampshire, England":"Southampton, Hampshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Alice Laton est née en 1444, à Lancashire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a eu au moins 1 fille avec Sir John Thornborough. Elle est décédée en 1500, à Essex, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, à l’âge de 56 ans."},"de":{"1444–1500":"1444–1500","1440–1531":"1440–1531","1467–Female":"1467–Verstorben","1467":"1467","1500":"1500","1444":"1444","1531":"15